data.description: Come view this beautiful Cape Cod home ins the Riverfront Community in Norfolk. The neighborhood is conveniently located near schools, employment centers, and other major support facilities. This home comes with granite countertops in the kitchen equipped with appliances, a gas range oven, butcher block, and dual ovens. If you like to entertain this kitchen is for you. Hardwood flooring throughout most of the home and a finished basement which offers 2 additional bedrooms to this home and 1 full bathroom, a living room, laundry room, and additional storage space.
